Priority: optional
Maintainer: Debian Qt/KDE Maintainers <debian-qt-kde@lists.debian.org>
Uploaders: Ana Beatriz Guerrero Lopez <ana@debian.org>, Sune Vuorela <debian@pusling.com>, Fathi Boudra <fabo@debian.org>, Armin Berres <trigger+debian@space-based.de>, Modestas Vainius <modestas@vainius.eu>, Matthew Rosewarne <mrosewarne@inoutbox.com>
Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 5), quilt, cmake, kdepimlibs5-dev (>= 4:4.0.0-1),
 libphonon-dev, libqimageblitz-dev, libsmbclient-dev, libusb-dev, libxkbfile-dev
